Who We Are

We are a team of passionate and experienced professionals who are committed to delivering excellence to our customers. We started our journey in 2005 with the vision of becoming a leading technology solutions provider in Ethiopia. Since then, we have grown into a company with over 1000 employees and 40 branch shops across the country.

Read More

Enterprise Solutions: We provide networking, remote communications, web application development, custom training, and internet solutions. We also specialize in systems integration and managed services.

Services

What We Do

We offer a wide range of technology solutions and consulting services that cater to different sectors and domains. Our solutions are designed to help businesses optimize their operations, reduce costs, and improve efficiency. Some of our key offerings are:

Financial Solutions: We provide mobile financial services, device financing, and digital payments. We are proud to be a master agent for Mpesa and have partnered with Safaricom to deliver innovative financial solutions.

Business Solutions: We provide CRM, SFA, BI, queue management, access control, and video surveillance solutions. We leverage our expertise in data analytics, security, and optimization to deliver customized solutions.

Read More

Products

What We Sell

We import and distribute a wide range of technology products and devices from some of the most reputable brands in the industry. Our products are designed to meet the needs of businesses across different sectors. Some of our key product categories are:

Computers and Laptops:

We offer enterprise computers, servers, desktop computers, and laptops from various brands such as Oracle, Huawei, HP, and Epson.

Mobile Devices and Accessories:

We offer mobile phones, tablets, dongles, routers, wireless cameras, and speakers from various brands such as Safaricom, Logitech, and Honeywell.

Printers and Scanners:

We offer label printers, industrial scanners, ID printers, and printers from various brands such as Epson, HP, and Honeywell.
